p: Would you like to access the PC to add Regigigas to your party?
\bI was hoping to complete the entire collection...
\bBut I guess it's worthless. Regigigas isn't a Delta Species, after all.
\bIt was a valiant attempt, \pn. I'll give you that.
\b... but Delta Species are the way of the future.
\bEven if you do get Regigigas on your side... you can't stop me.
\bEven you, the Augur, don't stand a chance against me. Not anymore!
\bLet me show you now, \pn! Let me show you my incredible power!
\bThat's impossible. My Deltas are superior! Unbeatable!
\bCheating is an academic offense warranting expulsion!
\bNevermind. I'll bide my time for now. I'll-
\bYou can't arrest me! I'm the leading researcher at Holon University!
\bI've won awards! I've captured legendaries! I have tenure!
\bLet's just make it easy on both of us, buster.
\rListen, \pn. I owe you one. Maybe two.
\rI can't really repay you for all you've done for Holon- helping us with our resource, exploring the region, and stopping Professor Maple.
\rListen, I'm sure you know about my Pokeball inventions.
\rIt's not much, but hopefully this can help you out.
\rThe Ancient Ball is as strong as an Ultra Ball, but if you use it on a legendary Pokemon, it has many times the catch rate.
\rThe idea of such a young Augur weirded me out at first, but, y'know...
\rIf anyone is worthy of that position, it's you.
\rHopefully you don't turn out to be a traitor too, eh?
